column5: I was going to fish the pool in the morning.Dont want to hike down if its mud.   Jeff
two of us are probably heading down in the morning.The more the merrier.Let you know in an hour or so.
I might fish the maid of the mist or the water out let. I think there will be to many people in the pool.   Jeff
jeff im leaving around 4 am or so, the niagara is blown right now as i hear. Might be a little better in Port
I will fish for Blue gills before I go to Port. Stop by we had a blast up on the Saugeen last weekend.   Jeff
